snippet.textDisplay: This could have been avoided if they would have done all this "quietly". Being impulsive has caused a media storm. His young family, Archie and Megan, would have been safer and more secure if they would have just discussed the situation with his royal family first. I'm sure to save them from the media storm the Queen, Prince Charles, Prince William and Prince Harry could have come up with a plan but dropping the news before telling his royal family was the wrong move. Impulsive and some would say intentionally done on the day before the Duchess of Cambridges Birthday. How could they not know what a media circus this would cause?
